name: Sunset
description:
Sunset
how do you pronounce
masculine name
1.
Sunset of a star on the horizon, especially that of the Sun.
"the sunset fires light the last roses"
two.
FORMAL
Decline or disappearance of something.
"twilight of the roman empire"
In a figurative sense, sunset means the phase of decline, decline, decline, decline, diminution, retreat or loss of strength or importance, the final stage or end of something. The sunset defines the period before the end of an event or the fall of something that was important or famous. It is also synonymous with ruin or death.
